                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-215" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM POCOCK</persName>
                  </hi>. I produce a certificate of Lloyd's former convic<lb></lb>tion, which I got from Mr. Clark's office (<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
